    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Process whereby the metals to be joined are dipped into a bath of molten salt, which acts as both flux and a source of heat.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
